{"tid":517117,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"其實宗教的本質","createTime":"2018-01-02T04:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T06:32:17.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fa451b128f2ae3c5499252949b94edda985df332","tid":517117,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T04:11:25.000Z","msg":"會唔會係上帝、神靈或外星人或其他超自然力量，為左針對人類社會，所設計的實驗項目？<br />\n<br />\n所以，信宗教，有人有宗教體驗/通靈經驗/神蹟/信仰治療，實在係正常，係無錯。因為除左心理作用或做假外，也有神靈干預。<br />\n<br />\n但唔好咁單純天真， 以為宗教有上帝和神靈的工作，就代表宗教必定係真。唔好咁天真認為，真係可以靠信心和敬虔，得救上天堂。"},{"pid":"ff015714e8ee5a433bf35205f405c0d7d33b3264","tid":517117,"uid":22040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"尼采話上帝已死<br />\n但有啲香港人就信上帝早已預備<br />\n試下睇呢篇，入門野<br />\n<a href=\"https://philosophy.hk01.com/channel/文章/51329/尼采：上帝之死---EP60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphilosophy.hk01.com%2Fchannel%2F%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%2F51329%2F%E5%B0%BC%E9%87%87%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%9D%E4%B9%8B%E6%AD%BB---EP60&d=UDIQJymwEHBoyuOaXPHGJRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=d3ac7e0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://philosophy.hk01.com/channel/文章/51329/尼采：上帝之死---EP60</a>"},{"pid":"a68e7c41051d4f0564aae4eb0a22901e257cd847","tid":517117,"uid":69484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"其實係當權者用黎和諧社會既手段 <br />\n對民眾黎講 係心靈既寄託 <br />\n唔係信既人傻 <br />\n如果假 點解唔封曬佢 <br />\n因為假唔假根本唔重要"},{"pid":"28e046c59ad8b540aef24ddd0ad9fb167822656b","tid":517117,"uid":22692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T04:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尼采話上帝已死<br />\n但有啲香港人就信上帝早已預備<br />\n試下睇呢篇，入門野<br />\n<a href=\"https://philosophy.hk01.com/channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphilosophy.hk01.com%2Fchannel%2F&d=UDIQJymwEHBoyuOaXPHGJRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=10597b4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://philosophy.hk01.com/channel/</a>文章/51329/尼采：上帝之死---EP60</blockquote><br />\n哲學01<img src=\"/assets/